      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，基地址用mermaidchart.atlassian.net，项目前缀按标准格式。这样点击卡片可以直接跳转到Jira看详情。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ticketBaseUrl"
