      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，fl02的LMS门户指向内容CDN，这个方向对吗？让我再确认一下业务逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id6",
        "docs01"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我刚才说反了。id6是LMS门户，它应该指向内容CDN，表示LMS门户依赖内容CDN提供资源，这个方向是对的。但id6的标注需要确认是Education_ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
