    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，id6的指向目标是Education_ContentCDN，和docs01一致。那docs01的指向目标是Education_LMS_Portal，两者形成交叉依赖，这符合CDN和门户的实际部署关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
